offers campaigns easily into

00:12:35.900 --> 00:12:38.420
Wallet and not have to do
extensive point-of-sale

00:12:38.420 --> 00:12:39.480
integrations.

00:12:39.480 --> 00:12:44.150
And what we're focused on is
making it super simple for

00:12:44.150 --> 00:12:46.230
merchants to take advantage of
these programs, with either

00:12:46.230 --> 00:12:48.980
doing no integration at all
and just leveraging their

00:12:48.980 --> 00:12:52.180
existing card network processing
that they already

00:12:52.180 --> 00:12:54.400
have in place.

00:12:54.400 --> 00:12:57.290
