it easy for airlines,

00:13:10.450 --> 00:13:16.030
transit providers, other types
of issuers of credentials,

00:13:16.030 --> 00:13:19.870
make it super simple for them
to get their credentials

00:13:19.870 --> 00:13:22.570
stored in the Wallet.

00:13:22.570 --> 00:13:25.970
And then this is where we kind
